{"type": "article", "id": 22385, "title": "可拼成茶几的边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-17T07:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606145506h5OJBHzxkcnGiqRU.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">瑞典设计师 Jonas Lindvall 为家具品牌 stolab 带来一组边桌，有三种材料的圆桌面，包括实心橡木、carrara（卡拉拉）的白色大理石和绿色大理石，搭配三根橡木桌腿，简单而自然。这三组边桌有三种不同的型号，恰好可以错位重叠在一起组成新的茶几组。具有北欧家具外形简单而又能灵活改变的特征。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145505GMbSQdHZwVvjU7yI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.52322738\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145505qDF6AePlEbJO8zKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68337408\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606145506VSfQ6cUPKe04Ei3R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}